{"tid":820623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風天買多幾日餸喺屋企 某啲Child 登仔又係到大驚小怪","createTime":"2018-09-15T13:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:23:01.000Z","uid":63452,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f16c427a6ac5e1fa8ba01d39792b9d73c5cb049f","tid":820623,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"淨係玩都有兩個post 話香港人喺超市盲搶<br />\n唔知佢地係咪無買過餸定無經歷過香港颱風<br />\n正常一個家庭一到打風都會買多幾日餸，日用品同乾糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時打風可能冇乜人喺屋企食， 一到打風全家人三餐都要喺屋企搞掂<br />\n我當你一家三口，當個風影響你三日，你老母都要煮多27 人份嘢食<br />\n正常超級市場又唔會隨時準備咁多貨預備打風，咁每家每戶買多幾日嘅存貨， 超級市場入面啲嘢畀人掃曬根本好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea98198e0483864f14b66691592afb943d3bf95","tid":820623,"uid":63452,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔又話人盲搶<br />\n但係盲搶鹽根本係無理嘅恐慌而囤積食鹽， 但係今次打風係超級市場嘅現像根本係正常家庭未雨綢繆，兩樣嘢冇得比<br />\n<br />\n有個post仲好笑，樓主自己係超級市場影個貨架話無嘢買，根本好大可能係佢自己都係plan 定去入貨，但係又唔夠人快俾人捷足先登， 然後就喺度嬲嬲豬影相上連登屌香港人盲搶<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/214909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F214909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e4b61abd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"766b8340dbafb8c65279e226f23c03be79c28ab5","tid":820623,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頂多星期日掛十號啫<br />\n<br />\n星期一都落波要返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c78eead328b8ec8486ac81852a238afd18b1b9","tid":820623,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:55:02.000Z","msg":"最癲係有人屌點解要&ldquo;盲搶&rdquo;新鮮餸，唔一早去買乾糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬個個一大風就走去餐餐食營多，到時營多冇貨，你咪又喺度屌人盲搶曬你啲營多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5b24985c227b0423cead6840b5c7b83329a1f9","tid":820623,"uid":63452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"766b8340dbafb8c65279e226f23c03be79c28ab5","tid":820623,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頂多星期日掛十號啫<br />\n<br />\n星期一都落波要返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"可能超市返唔切貨<br />\n可能你樓下個街市街市未開<br />\n可能停電啲肉類菜類壞曬<br />\n可能打風之後啲菜貴咗<br />\n<br />\n個風打幾個鐘都好，帶嚟嘅影響可能會有幾日，你唔會知"},{"pid":"e3d59e96515f096dc5afcc7dd277c2230e7ce400","tid":820623,"uid":197157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b5b24985c227b0423cead6840b5c7b83329a1f9","tid":820623,"uid":63452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"766b8340dbafb8c65279e226f23c03be79c28ab5","tid":820623,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頂多星期日掛十號啫<br />\n<br />\n星期一都落波要返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"可能超市返唔切貨<br />\n可能你樓下個街市街市未開<br />\n可能停電啲肉類菜類壞曬<br />\n可能打風之後啲菜貴咗<br />\n<br />\n個風打幾個鐘都好，帶嚟嘅影響可能會有幾日，你唔會知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"影響都可能幾個禮拜，買幾日咁少？"},{"pid":"131bb644e45b227f57a06929749662d90060ee70","tid":820623,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"打風姐 唔係打仗呀香港人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bAEsKS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bAEsKS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n香港人 洗唔撚洗買到咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"ht